dmca.title: Zanpakuto complains of Dugg copy
dmca.body:
The following story was dug for the purpose of sending traffic to a spam site. The content dug was illegally plagiarized from my site at Zanpakuto.com. I respectfully request removal of this article from Digg.com as soon as possible and, at the discretion of Digg administration, advise suspending this user for spam activities.

http://digg.com/comics_animation/Naruto_Shippuuden_48

~[private]

 Admin, Zanpakuto.com
